            "stanza_text": "Mettez le filet et la rame et les voiles,\nPêcheurs, au-dessus de ce tombeau marin\nOù dort Pélagôn, fils errant des étoiles"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Ce Mort a connu les hasards de l’orage,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Le tourment des flots, les monstres de la mer,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "La faim qui menace et la soif qui ravage",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ce Mort a connu les hasards de l’orage,\nLe tourment des flots, les monstres de la mer,\nLa faim qui menace et la soif qui ravage"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Mais le vent du large a gonflé sa poitrine",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "D’un souffle pareil à l’haleine des Dieux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Et les pieds d’argent de Téthys la divine",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Mais le vent du large a gonflé sa poitrine\nD’un souffle pareil à l’haleine des Dieux,\nEt les pieds d’argent de Téthys la divine"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Il a bu l’odeur et la couleur des vagues,",
